remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b1678-102">使用此属性可指定实体类的某个成员表示数据库表中的列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b1678-102">Use this attribute to designate a member of an entity class to represent a column in a database table.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b1678-103">可以将此特性应用于任何 `public`、`private`或 `internal`的字段或属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b1678-103">You can apply this attribute to any field or property that is `public`, `private`, or `internal`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b1678-104">[!INCLUDE[vbtecdlinq](~/includes/vbtecdlinq-md.md)] 保存对数据库所做的更改时，只会保留标识为列的实体类成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b1678-104">Only those entity class members identified as columns are persisted when [!INCLUDE[vbtecdlinq](~/includes/vbtecdlinq-md.md)] saves changes to the database.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b1678-105">使用逗号分隔特性上的多个属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b1678-105">Use commas to separate multiple properties on the attribute.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
<Table(Name:="Employees")>  _  
Public Class Employees  
    Private _LastName As String  
    ' …  
    <Column(Storage:="_LastName", DbType:="NVarChar(20) NOT NULL", _  
        CanBeNull:=false)> _  
    Public Property LastName() As String  
        Get  
            Return Me._LastName  
        End Get  
        Set  
            If ((Me._LastName = value) _  
                = false) Then  
                Me.OnPropertyChanging("LastName")  
                Me._LastName = value  
                Me.OnPropertyChanged("LastName")  
            End If  
        End Set  
    End Property  
End Class  
```  
  
```csharp  
[Table(Name="Employees")]  
public class Employees  
{  
    private string _LastName;      
    // …  
    [Column(Storage="_LastName", DbType="NVarChar(20) NOT NULL",   
        CanBeNull=false)]  
    public string LastName  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return this._LastName;  
        }  
        set  
        {  
            if ((this._LastName != value))  
            {  
                this.OnPropertyChanging("LastName");  
                this._LastName = value;  
                this.OnPropertyChanged("LastName");  
            }  
        }  
    }  
}  
```
